thread.title: Robyn Cowell
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Robyn Cowell

author: Robyn Cowell
title: Robyn Cowell
text: I have used Ink Station for about three years. The web site is extremely simple to navigate and very easy to order from. In the event where I needed to speak to someone by phone there was no problem reaching them and my question was answered there and then. I chose to use non genuine products. I have had only one cartridge which I wasn't able to use during this time. I have no reservations in recommending Ink Station.
